Package io.github.beanbeanjuice.cafeapi.exception

package io.github.beanbeanjuice.cafeapi.exception
  • Exception Summary
    Exception
    Description
    AuthorizationException
    A CafeException used when a Request responds with a status code of 401.
    CafeException
    A generic RuntimeException used for CafeAPI exceptions.
    ConflictException
    A CafeException used when a Request responds with a status code of 409.
    NotFoundException
    A CafeException used when a Request responds with a status code of 404.
    ResponseException
    A CafeException used when a Request responds with a status code of 500.
    TeaPotException
    An CafeException that is thrown when mismatched variables are present.
    UndefinedVariableException
    A CafeException used when a Request responds with a status code of 400.
